strings: <voice_0x01000D5B><se_low>January: We have the container! It is said to contain Venus's tears. It must be a real diamond!
<voice_0x01000D5C><se_low>January: This is not the first entry to this position. I've never been near the box.
<voice_0x01000D5D><se_low>January: But this time I give up! I'm studying for a gold star!
